<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早安！<tag a="110" b="4" />。<10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然現在還很早，<delay20 />
但我不知道為什麼就醒來了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過採取與平常不同的行動<delay20 />
有種新鮮的感覺，也挺不錯呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總覺得內心忐忑不安，<delay20 />
所以才會這麼早就醒來。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果就遇到你了！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把沉睡的<tag a="110" b="10" />
喚醒的人<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或許就是你呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Good Morning！<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然今天起得比平常早，<delay20 />
但這是因為我大清早的腳就抽筋，<delay20 />
醒來以後乾脆直接起床了。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 />或許是某個人的思念<delay20 />
喚醒了沉睡的<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="10" />呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得<delay20 />
今天還不想睡覺呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過啊，<delay20 />
我覺得在這種寂靜的時刻，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好好地面對自我也不錯喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay20 />
你睡不著嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我也是喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有時候我會覺得啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />深夜的寂靜被施了魔法，
讓人感覺這段時間沒有盡頭，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因此情緒也隨之高漲，<delay20 />
最後便徹夜未眠<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay20 />大概就是那種感覺～</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚安！<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總覺得今晚睡不著啊。<10_4 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也是嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你不嫌棄的話，要不要和我聊聊天？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這屬於大人的時刻<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>